# 1 - instale o cli de forma globa do grunt
- npm i -g grunt-cli

# 2 - Inicalize npm
- npm init

# 3 - Instale as dependencias do grunt
- npm i --save-dev grunt

# 4 - Istale as dependencias do LESS, SASS, e CONCURRENT
- npm i --save-dev grunt-contrib-less
- npm i --save-dev grunt-concurrent
- npm i --save-dev grunt-contrib-sass

obs.: tem que adicionar o script do grunt no package.json ("grunt": "grunt")